## <a name="brazil-national-identification-card-rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1522">Национальная идентификация Бразилии (RG)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1522">Brazil national identification card (RG)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1523">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1523">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1524">Реестр Geral (старый формат): девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1524">Registro Geral (old format): Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1525">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (новый формат): 11 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1525">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format): 11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1526">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1526">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1527">Registro Geral (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1527">Registro Geral (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1528">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1528">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1529">период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1529">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1530">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1530">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1531">период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1531">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1532">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1532">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1533">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1533">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1534">одна цифра, которая является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1534">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1535">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1535">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1536">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1536">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1537">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1537">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1538">одна цифра, которая является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1538">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1539">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1539">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1540">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1540">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1541">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1541">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1542">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1542">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1543">функция Func_brazil_rg находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1543">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1544">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_rg;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1544">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_rg is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1545">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1545">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- Brazil National ID Card (RG) -->
      <Entity id="486de900-db70-41b3-a886-abdf25af119c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_rg" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1546">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1546">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1547">Keyword_brazil_rg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1547">Keyword_brazil_rg</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1548">Cédula de identidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1548">Cédula de identidade</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1549">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1549">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1550">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1550">national id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1551">número de rregistro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1551">número de rregistro</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1552">registro de Iidentidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1552">registro de Iidentidade</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1553">registro geral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1553">registro geral</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1554">RG (это ключевое слово является чувствительным к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1554">RG (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1555">RIC (это ключевое слово является чувствительным к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1555">RIC (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span> 


## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1556">Номер водительского удостоверения Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1556">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1557">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1557">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1558">девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1558">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1559">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1559">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1560">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1560">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1561">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1561">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1562">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1562">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1563">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1563">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1564">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1564">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1565">Обычное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1565">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1566">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1566">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="66d39258-94c2-43b2-804b-aa312258e54b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>    
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1586">driverslicenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1586">driverslicenses</span></span>

## <a name="bulgaria-uniform-civil-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1693">Единый гражданский номер Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1693">Bulgaria uniform civil number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1694">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1694">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1695">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1695">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1696">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1696">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1697">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1697">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1698">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1698">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1699">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1699">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1700">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1700">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1701">10 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1701">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1702">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1702">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1703">10 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1703">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1704">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1704">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1705">две цифры, соответствующие порядку рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1705">two digits that correspond to the birth order</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1706">одна цифра, соответствующая полу: четная цифра для мужчин и нечетная цифра для женщин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1706">one digit that corresponds to gender: An even digit for male and an odd digit for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1707">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1707">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1708">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1708">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1709">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1709">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1710">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1710">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1711">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1711">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1712">Функция находит  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1712">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1713">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1713">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1714">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1714">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1715">Функция находит  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1715">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Uniform Civil Number -->
      <Entity id="100d58b1-0a35-4fb1-aa89-e4a86fb53fcc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1760">Номер паспорта Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1760">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1761">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1761">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1762">девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1762">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1763">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1763">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1764">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1764">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1765">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1765">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1766">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1766">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1767">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1767">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1768">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1768">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1769">Обычное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1769">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1770">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1770">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1771">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1771">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1772">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1772">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1773">Обычное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1773">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1774">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1774">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="f7172b82-c588-4216-845e-4e54e397f29a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1787">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1787">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1789">номер на паспорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1789">номер на паспорт</span></span>

## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1794">Номер банковского счета в Канаде</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1794">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1795">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1795">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1796">7 или 12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1796">7 or 12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1797">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1797">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1798">Номер учетной записи Банка Канады — 7 или 12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1798">A Canada Bank Account Number is 7 or 12 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1799">Транзитный номер банковского счета в Канаде имеет указанный ниже формат.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1799">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1800">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1800">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1801">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1801">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1802">три цифры OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1802">three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1803">нулевое значение "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1803">a zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1804">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1804">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1805">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1805">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1806">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1806">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1807">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1807">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1808">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1808">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1809">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1809">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1810">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1810">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1811">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1811">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1812">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1812">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1813">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1813">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1814">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1814">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1838">Номер водительских прав в Канаде</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1838">Canada driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1839">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1839">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1840">Зависит от провинции.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1840">Varies by province</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1841">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1841">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1842">Различные шаблоны, соответствующие провинциям Альберта, Британская Колумбия, Манитоба, Нью-Брансуик, Ньюфаундленд и Лабрадор, Новая Шотландия, Онтарио, Остров Принца Эдуарда, Квебек и Саскачеван.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1842">Various patterns covering Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Newfoundland/Labrador, Nova Scotia, Ontario, Prince Edward Island, Quebec, and Saskatchewan</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1843">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1843">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1844">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1844">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1845">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1845">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1846">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1846">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1847">функция Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1847">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1848">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1848">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1849">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1849">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="37186abb-8e48-4800-ad3c-e3d1610b3db0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">

        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />

      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">

        <Match idRef="Keyword_nova_scotia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ontario_drivers_license_number" />

      </Pattern>
```

## <a name="canada-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1985">Номер службы здравоохранения Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1985">Canada health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1986">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1986">Format</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1987">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1987">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1988">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1988">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1989">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1989">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1990">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1990">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1991">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1991">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1992">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1992">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1993">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1993">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1994">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_health_service_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1994">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-1995">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_health_service_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-1995">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
<Entity id="59c0bf39-7fab-482c-af25-00faa4384c94" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_health_service_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_health_service_number" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2001">speciality services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2001">speciality services</span></span>

## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2007">Номер паспорта Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2007">Canada passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2008">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2008">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2009">два верхних буквы с последующим шестью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2009">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2010">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2010">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2011">два верхних буквы с последующим шестью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2011">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2012">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2012">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2013">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2013">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2014">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2014">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2015">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2015">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2016">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2016">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2017">Найдено ключевое слово Keyword_canada_passport_number Keyword_passport или Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2017">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->
<Entity id="14d0db8b-498a-43ed-9fca-f6097ae687eb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-personal-health-identification-number-phin"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2047">Идентификационный номер личного здоровья Канады (PHIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2047">Canada personal health identification number (PHIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2048">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2048">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2049">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2049">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2050">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2050">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2051">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2051">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2052">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2052">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2053">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2053">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2054">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2054">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2055">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2055">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2056">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_phin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2056">The regular expression Regex_canada_phin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2057">Найдены по крайней мере два Keyword_canada_phin или Keyword_canada_provinces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2057">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada PHIN -->
<Entity id="722e12ac-c89a-4ec8-a1b7-fea3469f89db" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_phin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_phin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_provinces" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2090">Номер социального страхования Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2090">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2091">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2091">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2092">девять цифр с необязательными дефисами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2092">nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2093">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2093">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2094">Форматированный:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2094">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2095">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2095">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2096">дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2096">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2097">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2097">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2098">дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2098">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2099">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2099">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2100">Unformatted: nine digits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2100">Unformatted: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2101">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2101">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2102">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2102">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2103">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2103">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2104">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2104">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2105">Функция Func_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2105">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2106">Выполняются по меньшей мере два из таких условий:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2106">At least two of any combination of the following:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2107">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2107">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2108">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin_collaborative;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2108">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2109">функция Func_eu_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2109">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2110">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2110">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2111">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2111">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2112">функция Func_unformatted_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2112">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2113">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2113">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2114">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2114">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2139">Номер удостоверения личности в Чили</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2139">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2140">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2140">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2141">семь-восемь цифр плюс делимитеры контрольная цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2141">seven to eight digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2142">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2142">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2143">семь-восемь цифр плюс делимитеры:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2143">seven to eight digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2144">от одной до двух цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2144">one to two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2145">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2145">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2146">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2146">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2147">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2147">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2148">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2148">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2149">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2149">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2150">одна цифра или буква (не чувствительная к делу), которая является проверяемой цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2150">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2151">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2151">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2152">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2152">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2153">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2153">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2154">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2154">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2155">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2155">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2156">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_chile_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2156">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2157">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2157">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2158">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2158">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2159">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2159">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2160">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2160">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2197">Номер удостоверения резидента Китая (PRC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2197">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2198">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2198">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2199">18 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2199">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2200">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2200">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2201">18 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2201">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2202">шесть цифр, которые являются адресным кодом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2202">six digits that are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2203">восемь цифр в форме YYYYYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2203">eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2204">три цифры, которые являются кодом заказа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2204">three digits that are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2205">одна цифра, которая является контрольной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2205">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2206">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2206">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2207">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2207">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2208">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2208">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2209">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2209">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2210">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2210">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2211">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_china_resident_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2211">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2212">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2212">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2213">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2213">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2214">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2214">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2215">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2215">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2216">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2216">Keywords</span></span>

### <a name="keyword_china_resident_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2217">Keyword_china_resident_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2217">Keyword_china_resident_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2218">Resident Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2218">Resident Identity Card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2220">National Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2220">National Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2221">身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2221">身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2222">居民 身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2222">居民 身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2223">居民身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2223">居民身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2224">鉴定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2224">鉴定</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2225">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2225">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2226">居民 身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2226">居民 身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2227">鑑定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2227">鑑定</span></span> 

   
## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2228">Номер кредитной карты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2228">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2229">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2229">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2230">От 14 до 16 цифр, которые могут быть отформатированы или неформатированы (dddd), и которые должны пройти тест Luhn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2230">14 to 16 digits that can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and that must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2231">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2231">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2232">Сложный и надежный шаблон, который обнаруживает карты всех крупных брендов по всему миру, включая карты Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, подарочные карты и карточки для посетителей.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2232">Complex and robust pattern that detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2233">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2233">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2234">Да (рассчитывается по алгоритму Луна).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2234">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2235">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2235">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2236">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2236">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2237">Функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2237">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2238">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2238">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2239">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_verification;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2239">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2240">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2240">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2241">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2241">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2242">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2242">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2243">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2243">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2244">функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2244">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2245">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2245">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2506">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2506">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2507">восемь цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2507">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2508">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2508">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2511">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2511">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2512">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2512">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2513">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2513">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2514">Обычное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2514">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2515">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2515">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="005b3ef1-47dd-4e68-bb02-c6db484d00f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2639">Номер удостоверения личности в Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2639">Croatia identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2640">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации входит в тип конфиденциальной информации о номере национальной идентификации ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2640">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2641">Он доступен в виде отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2641">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2642">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2642">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2643">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2643">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2644">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2644">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2645">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2645">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2646">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2646">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2647">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2647">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2648">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2648">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2649">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2649">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2650">функция Func_croatia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2650">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2651">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_croatia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2651">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Croatia Identity Card Number-->
<Entity id="ff12f884-c20a-4189-b185-34c8e7258d47" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2682">Номер паспорта Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2682">Croatia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2683">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2683">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2684">девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2684">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2685">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2685">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2686">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2686">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2687">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2687">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2688">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2688">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2689">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2689">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2690">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2690">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2691">Обычное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2691">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2692">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2692">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2693">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2693">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2694">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2694">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2695">Обычное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2695">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2696">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2696">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Croatia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7d7a729d-32d8-4204-8d01-d5e6a6c25581" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2697">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2697">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2702">паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2702">passports</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2706">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2706">passport number</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2709">Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2709">Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2710">broj putovnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2710">broj putovnice</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2713">br putovnice</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2713">br putovnice</span></span>
   
## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2714">Личный идентификационный номер (OIB) в Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2714">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2715">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2715">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2716">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2716">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2717">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2717">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2718">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2718">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2719">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2719">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2720">окончательная цифра — это контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2720">final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2721">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2721">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2722">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2722">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2723">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2723">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2724">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2724">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2725">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2725">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2726">Ключевое слово из Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2726">A keyword from Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2727">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2727">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2728">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2728">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2729">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2729">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2730">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2730">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
      <Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2731">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2731">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2761">Номер лицензии для водителей Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2761">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2762">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2762">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2763">12 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2763">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2764">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2764">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2765">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2765">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2766">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2766">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2767">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2767">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2768">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2768">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2769">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2769">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2770">Обычное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2770">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2771">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2771">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="356fa104-f9ac-4aff-a0e4-2e6e65ea06c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2896">Удостоверение личности на Кипре</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2896">Cyprus identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2897">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2897">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2898">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2898">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2899">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2899">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2900">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2900">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2901">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2901">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2902">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2902">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2903">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2903">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2904">10 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2904">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2905">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2905">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2906">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2906">10 digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2907">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2907">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2908">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2908">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2909">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2909">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2910">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2910">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2911">Обычное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2911">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2912">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2912">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
      <!-- Cyprus Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="3ba8afe5-7a6c-4929-8247-0001b6878438" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2913">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2913">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2914">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2914">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-2915">номер id-карты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-2915">id card number</span></span>
