## <a name="france-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4654">Номер медицинского страхования Во Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4654">France health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4655">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4655">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4656">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4656">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4657">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4657">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4658">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4658">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4659">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4659">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4660">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4660">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4661">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4661">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4662">21-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4662">21-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4663">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4663">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4664">21-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4664">21-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4665">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4665">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4666">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4666">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4667">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4667">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4668">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4668">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4669">цифру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4669">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4670">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4670">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4671">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4671">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4672">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4672">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4673">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4673">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4674">regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4674">the regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4675">найдено ключевое слово Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4675">a keyword from Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="9bc2069e-76df-4ff9-ac02-2f519469e236" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4676">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4676">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_health_insurance_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4677">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4677">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4678">карта страхования</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4678">insurance card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4679">carte vitale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4679">carte vitale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4680">carte d'assuré social</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4680">carte d'assuré social</span></span>


## <a name="france-national-id-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4681">Национальная id-карта Франции (CNI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4681">France national id card (CNI)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4682">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4682">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4683">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4683">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4684">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4684">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4685">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4685">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4686">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4686">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4687">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4687">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4688">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4688">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4689">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4689">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4690">регулярное выражение Regex_france_cni находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4690">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4691">Ключевое слово Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4691">A keyword from Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France CNI -->
    <Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4696">carte nationale d'idenite no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4696">carte nationale d'idenite no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4697">cni #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4697">cni#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4701">национальная идентичность</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4701">national identity</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4704">numéro de carte vitale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4704">numéro de carte vitale</span></span>

   
## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4705">Номер паспорта Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4705">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4706">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4706">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4707">Он доступен в виде отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4707">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4708">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4708">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4709">девять цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4709">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4710">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4710">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4711">девять цифр и букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4711">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4712">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4712">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4713">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4713">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4714">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4714">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4715">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4715">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4716">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4716">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4717">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4717">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4718">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4718">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4719">Функция находит `Func_fr_passport` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4719">The function `Func_fr_passport` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4720">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4720">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4721">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате DD MM YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4721">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4722">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4722">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4723">Функция находит `Func_fr_passport` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4723">The function `Func_fr_passport` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4724">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4724">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- France Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4755">Номер социального обеспечения Франции (INSEE)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4755">France social security number (INSEE)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4756">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4756">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4757">15 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4757">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4758">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4758">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4759">Должен соответствовать одному из двух шаблонов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4759">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4760">13 цифр с последующим пространством с двумя цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4760">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4761">или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4761">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4762">15 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4762">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4763">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4763">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4764">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4764">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4765">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4765">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4766">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4766">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4767">Функция находит `Func_french_insee` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4767">The function `Func_french_insee` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4768">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4768">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4769">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4769">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4770">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4770">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4771">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4771">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4772">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4772">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France INSEE -->
    <Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4773">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4773">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_fr_insee"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4774">Keyword_fr_insee</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4774">Keyword_fr_insee</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4778">fssn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4778">fssn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4779">le numéro d'identification nationale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4779">le numéro d'identification nationale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4780">le code de la sécurité sociale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4780">le code de la sécurité sociale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4781">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4781">national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4782">national identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4782">national identification</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-p133">
no. d'identité</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-p133">no. d'identité</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4786">numéro d'assurance</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4786">numéro d'assurance</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4788">numero d'identite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4788">numero d'identite</span></span>

no. d'identite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-p134">no. d'identite</span></span>

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4803">Номер идентификации налога во Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4803">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4804">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4804">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4805">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4805">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4806">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4806">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4807">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4807">13 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4808">Одна цифра, которая должна быть 0, 1, 2 или 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4808">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4809">Одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4809">One digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4810">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4810">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4811">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4811">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4812">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4812">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4813">три цифры; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4813">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4814">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4814">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4815">три цифры; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4815">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4816">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4816">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4817">Три контрольных цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4817">Three check digits</span></span> 

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4818">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4818">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4819">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4819">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4820">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4820">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4821">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4821">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4822">Функция находит  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4822">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4823">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4823">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4824">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4824">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4825">Функция находит  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4825">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4826">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4826">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4827">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4827">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4828">numéro d'identification fiscale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4828">numéro d'identification fiscale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4829">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4829">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4830">идентификация налога нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4830">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4831">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4831">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4832">нет налога #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4832">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4833">нет налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4833">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4834">налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4834">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4835">номер регистрации налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4835">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4836">таксомоторный #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4836">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4837">taxidno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4837">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4838">taxidnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4838">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4839">taxno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4839">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4840">taxnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4840">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4841">taxnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4841">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4842">tin id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4842">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4843">олово нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4843">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4844">олово #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4844">tin#</span></span>


## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4845">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость во Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4845">France value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4846">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4846">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4847">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4847">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4848">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4848">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4849">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4849">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4850">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4850">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4851">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4851">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4852">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4852">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4853">13 символов альфанумерного шаблона</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4853">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4854">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4854">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4855">13 символов альфанумерного шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4855">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4856">две буквы - FR (случай нечувствительный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4856">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4857">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4857">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4858">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4858">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4859">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4859">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4860">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4860">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4861">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4861">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4862">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4862">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4863">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4863">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4864">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4864">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4865">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4865">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4866">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4866">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4867">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4867">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4868">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4868">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4869">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4869">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4870">Найдено ключевое слово Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4870">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4871">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4871">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4872">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4872">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4873">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4873">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4874">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4874">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4875">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4875">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4876">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4876">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4877">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4877">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4878">налог на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4878">value added tax</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4879">идентификация сирены без numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4879">siren identification no numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4880">taxe valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4880">taxe valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4881">taxe sur la valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4881">taxe sur la valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4882">n° tva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4882">n° tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4883">numéro de tva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4883">numéro de tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4884">сирена numéro d'identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4884">numéro d'identification siren</span></span>


## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4885">Номер водительских прав в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4885">Germany driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4886">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации входит в тип конфиденциальной информации номер лицензии водителя ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4886">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4887">Он доступен в виде отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4887">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4888">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4888">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4889">сочетание 11 цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4889">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4890">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4890">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4891">11 цифр и букв (не чувствительных к делу):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4891">11 digits and letters (not case-sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4892">цифру или букву</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4892">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4893">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4893">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4894">шесть цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4894">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4895">цифру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4895">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4896">цифру или букву</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4896">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4897">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4897">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4898">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4898">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4899">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4899">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4900">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4900">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4901">Функция Func_german_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4901">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4902">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4902">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-4903">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-4903">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5052">Номер удостоверения личности в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5052">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5053">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5053">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5054">с 1 ноября 2010 г.: девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5054">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5055">с 1 апреля 1987 г. по 31 октября 2010 г.: 10 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5055">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5056">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5056">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5057">с 1 ноября 2010 г.:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5057">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5058">одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5058">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5059">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5059">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5060">с 1 апреля 1987 г. по 31 октября 2010 г.:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5060">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5061">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5061">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5062">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5062">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5063">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5063">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5064">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5064">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5065">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5065">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5066">регулярное выражение Regex_germany_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5066">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5067">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_germany_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5067">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5068">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5068">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5069">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5069">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5072">идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5072">identification</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5074">identifizierungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5074">identifizierungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5075">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5075">identity card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5081">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5081">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5082">persönliche-id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5082">persönliche-id-nummer</span></span>


## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5083">Номер паспорта Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5083">Germany passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5084">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации входит в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5084">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5085">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5085">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5086">10 цифр или букв.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5086">10 digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5087">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5087">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5088">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5088">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5089">первый символ — это цифры или буквы из этого набора (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5089">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5090">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5090">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5091">пять цифр или букв из этого набора (C, H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5091">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5092">цифру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5092">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5093">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5093">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5094">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5094">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5095">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5095">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5096">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5096">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5097">функция Func_german_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5097">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5098">Ключевое слово `Keyword_german_passport` из `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5098">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5099">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5099">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5100">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5100">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5101">функция Func_german_passport_data находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5101">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5102">Ключевое слово `Keyword_german_passport` из `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5102">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5103">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5103">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5124">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5124">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5125">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5125">passport numbers</span></span>


## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5126">Идентификационный номер налога в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5126">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5127">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5127">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5128">11 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5128">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5129">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5129">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5130">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5130">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5131">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5131">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5132">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5132">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5133">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5133">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5134">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5134">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5135">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5135">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5136">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5136">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5137">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5137">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5138">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5138">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5139">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5139">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5140">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5140">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5141">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5141">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5142">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5142">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5143">Функция находит  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5143">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5144">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5144">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5145">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5145">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5146">Функция находит  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5146">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5147">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5147">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5151">steueridentifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5151">steueridentifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5152">steuernummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5152">steuernummer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5154">идентификация налога нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5154">tax identification no</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5156">нет налога #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5156">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5157">нет налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5157">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5158">налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5158">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5159">номер регистрации налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5159">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5160">таксомоторный #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5160">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5161">taxidno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5161">taxidno#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5163">taxno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5163">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5164">taxnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5164">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5165">taxnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5165">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5166">tin id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5166">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5167">олово нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5167">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5168">олово #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5168">tin#</span></span>

## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5172">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5172">Germany value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5173">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5173">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5174">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5174">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5175">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5175">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5176">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5176">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5177">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5177">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5178">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5178">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5179">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5179">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5180">Альфанумерный шаблон 11 символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5180">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5181">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5181">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5182">11-символ альфанумерного шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5182">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5183">буква D или d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5183">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5184">письмо E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5184">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5185">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5185">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5186">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5186">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5187">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5187">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5188">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5188">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5189">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5189">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5190">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5190">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5191">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5191">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5192">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5192">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5193">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5193">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5194">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5194">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5195">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5195">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5196">Ключевое слово Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5196">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5197">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5197">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5198">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5198">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5199">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5199">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5200">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5200">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5201">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5201">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5202">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5202">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5203">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5203">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5204">vat# mehrwertsteuer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5204">vat#  mehrwertsteuer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5205">mwst</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5205">mwst</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5206">mehrwertsteuer identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5206">mehrwertsteuer identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5207">nummer mehrwertsteuer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5207">mehrwertsteuer nummer</span></span>


## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5208">Номер водительских прав Греции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5208">Greece driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5209">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации входит в тип конфиденциальной информации номер лицензии водителя ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5209">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5210">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5210">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5211">девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5211">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5212">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5212">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5213">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5213">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5214">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5214">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5215">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5215">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5216">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5216">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5217">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5217">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5218">Обычное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5218">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5219">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5219">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="7a2200b5-aacf-4e3c-ab36-136d3e68b7da" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5220">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5220">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5221">Keywords_eu_driver s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5221">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>
