## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5345">Национальная ID-карта Греции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5345">Greece national ID card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5346">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5346">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5347">Сочетание 7–8 букв и чисел, а также тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5347">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5348">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5348">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5349">Семь букв и чисел (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5349">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5350">одна буква (любая буква греческого алфавита);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5350">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5351">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5351">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5352">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5352">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5353">Восемь букв и чисел (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5353">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5354">две буквы, которые в прописном виде есть как в греческом, так и латинском алфавите (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5354">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5355">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5355">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5356">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5356">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5357">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5357">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5358">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5358">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5359">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5359">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5360">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5360">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5361">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5361">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5362">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_greece_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5362">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5363">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5363">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5364">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5364">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5365">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5365">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_greece_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5366">Keyword_greece_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5366">Keyword_greece_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5367">греческий id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5367">greek id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5368">греческий национальный id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5368">greek national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5369">греческая личная id-карта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5369">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5370">греческий id полиции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5370">greek police id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5371">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5371">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5372">tautotita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5372">tautotita</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5373">ταυτότητα</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5373">ταυτότητα</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5374">ταυτότητας</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5374">ταυτότητας</span></span>


## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5375">Номер паспорта Греции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5375">Greece passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5376">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5376">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5377">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5377">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5378">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5378">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5379">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5379">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5380">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5380">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5381">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5381">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5382">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5382">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5383">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5383">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5384">Обычное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5384">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5385">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5385">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5386">Регулярное выражение находит дату `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` в формате DD MMM YY (Пример - 28 августа 19) или ключевое слово `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5386">The regular expression `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM YY (Example - 28 Aug 19) or a keyword from `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5387">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5387">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5388">Обычное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5388">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5389">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5389">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7e65eb47-cdf9-4f52-8f90-2a27d5ee67e3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5390">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5390">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5391">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5391">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5392">паспорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5392">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5393">паспорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5393">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5394">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5394">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5395">паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5395">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5396">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5396">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5397">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5397">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5398">passportnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5398">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5399">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5399">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5400">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5400">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5401">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5401">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5402">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5402">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5403">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5403">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5404">αριθμούς διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5404">αριθμούς διαβατηρίου</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5405">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5405">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span></span>


## <a name="greece-social-security-number-amka"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5406">Номер социального обеспечения Греции (AMKA)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5406">Greece Social Security Number (AMKA)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5407">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5407">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5408">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5408">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5409">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5409">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5410">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5410">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5411">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5411">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5412">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5412">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5413">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5413">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5414">Одиннадцать цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5414">Eleven digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5415">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5415">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5416">6 цифр как дата рождения YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5416">6 digits as date of birth YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5417">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5417">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5418">контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5418">a check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5419">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5419">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5420">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5420">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5421">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5421">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5422">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5422">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5423">Функция находит  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5423">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5424">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5424">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5425">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5425">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5426">Функция находит  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5426">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Greece Social Security Number (AMKA) -->
      <Entity id="e39b03f4-50ea-41ae-af7a-a4b9539596ad" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5427">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5427">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5428">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5428">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5429">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5429">ssn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5430">ssn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5430">ssn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5431">социального обеспечения нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5431">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5432">socialsecurityno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5432">socialsecurityno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5433">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5433">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5434">amka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5434">amka</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5435">a.m.k.a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5435">a.m.k.a.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5436">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5436">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span></span>


## <a name="greece-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5437">Идентификационный номер налога в Греции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5437">Greece tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5438">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5438">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5439">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5439">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5440">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5440">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5441">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5441">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5442">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5442">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5443">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5443">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5444">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5444">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5445">Девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5445">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5446">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5446">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5447">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5447">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5448">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5448">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5449">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5449">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5450">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5450">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5451">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5451">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5452">Обычное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5452">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5453">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5453">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greek Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="15a54a5a-53d4-4080-ad43-a2a4fe1d3bf7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5482">Номер удостоверения личности Гонконга (HKID)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5482">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5483">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5483">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5484">Сочетание 8–9 букв и чисел, а также необязательные скобки вокруг последнего символа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5484">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5485">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5485">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5486">Сочетание 8–9 букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5486">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5487">1-2 буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5487">1-2 letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5488">шесть цифр; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5488">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5489">последний символ (любая цифра или буква "A") является проверочной цифрой и заключен в скобки (необязательно).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5489">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5490">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5490">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5491">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5491">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5492">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5492">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5493">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5493">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5494">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5494">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5495">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_hong_kong_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5495">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5496">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5496">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5497">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5497">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5498">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5498">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5499">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5499">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5539">Номер водительских прав в Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5539">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5540">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5540">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5541">Две буквы с шестью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5541">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5542">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5542">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5543">Две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5543">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5544">Две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5544">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5545">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5545">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5546">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5546">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5547">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5547">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5548">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5548">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5549">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5549">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5550">Обычное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5550">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5551">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5551">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <Entity id="9d31c46b-6e6b-444c-aeb1-6dd7e604bb24" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5676">Личный идентификационный номер Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5676">Hungary personal identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5677">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5677">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5678">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5678">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5679">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5679">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5680">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5680">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5681">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5681">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5682">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5682">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5683">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5683">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5684">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5684">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5685">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5685">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5686">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5686">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5687">Одна цифра, соответствующая полу (1-мужская, 2-женская, другие номера также возможны для граждан, родившихся до 1900 г. или граждан с двойным гражданством)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5687">One digit that corresponds to gender (1-male, 2-female, other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5688">Шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5688">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5689">Три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5689">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5690">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5690">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5691">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5691">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5692">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5692">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5693">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5693">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5694">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5694">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5695">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5695">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5696">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5696">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5697">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5697">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5698">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5698">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="7b5cc218-7046-47d9-80c9-f325b50896ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5699">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5699">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5700">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5700">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5701">номер id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5701">id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5702">identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5702">identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5703">sz ig</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5703">sz ig</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5704">sz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5704">sz.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5705">ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5705">ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5706">sz.ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5706">sz.ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5707">személyazonosító igazolvány</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5707">személyazonosító igazolvány</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5708">személyi igazolvány</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5708">személyi igazolvány</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5709">Номер паспорта Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5709">Hungary passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5710">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5710">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5711">Две буквы с шестью или семью цифрами без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5711">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5712">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5712">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5713">Две буквы с шестью или семью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5713">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5714">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5714">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5715">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5715">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5716">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5716">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5717">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5717">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5718">Обычное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5718">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5719">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5719">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5720">Обычное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YY (Пример - 01 MÁR/MAR 12) или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из найдено</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5720">The regular expression `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YY (Example - 01 MÁR/MAR 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5721">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5721">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5722">Обычное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5722">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5723">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5723">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5b483910-9aa7-4c99-9917-f4001464bda7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5724">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5724">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5725">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5725">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5727">паспорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5727">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5728">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5728">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5729">паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5729">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5730">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5730">passportno</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5732">passportnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5732">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5733">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5733">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5734">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5734">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5735">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5735">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5736">Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5736">Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5737">útlevél száma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5737">útlevél száma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5738">Útlevelek száma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5738">Útlevelek száma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5739">útlevél szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5739">útlevél szám</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_date"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5740">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5740">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5741">дата выпуска</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5741">date of issue</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5742">дата истечения срока действия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5742">date of expiry</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-social-security-number-taj"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5743">Номер социального обеспечения Венгрии (TAJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5743">Hungary social security number (TAJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5744">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5744">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5745">Девять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5745">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5746">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5746">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5747">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5747">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5748">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5748">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5749">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5749">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5750">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5750">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5751">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5751">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5752">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5752">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5753">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5753">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5754">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5754">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5755">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5755">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Social Security Number (TAJ) -->
      <Entity id="0de78315-9537-47f5-95ab-b3e77eba3993" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5756">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5756">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5775">Идентификация налога в Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5775">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5776">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5776">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5777">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5777">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5778">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5778">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5779">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5779">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5780">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5780">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5781">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5781">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5782">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5782">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5783">10 цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5783">10 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5784">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5784">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5785">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5785">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5786">Одна цифра, которая должна быть "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5786">One digit that must be "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5787">Восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5787">Eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5788">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5788">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5789">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5789">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5790">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5790">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5791">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5791">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5792">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5792">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5793">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5793">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5794">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5794">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5795">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5795">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5796">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5796">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="ede42eb4-59d9-49eb-9603-d7853fbda91d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5822">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5822">Hungary value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5823">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5823">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5824">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5824">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5825">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5825">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5826">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5826">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5827">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5827">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5828">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5828">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5829">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5829">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5830">Альфанумерный шаблон 10 символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5830">10 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5831">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5831">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5832">10 символов альфанумерного шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5832">10 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5833">две буквы - HU или hu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5833">two letters - HU or hu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5834">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5834">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5835">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5835">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5836">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5836">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5837">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5837">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5838">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5838">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5839">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5839">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5840">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5840">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5841">Ключевое слово Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5841">A keyword from Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5842">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5842">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5843">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5843">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="976349a0-683b-477a-90f8-ff0a220d5592" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5844">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5844">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_hungary_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5845">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5845">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-5848">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-5848">vat#</span></span>
