## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6584">Номер банковского счета в Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6584">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6585">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6585">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6586">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6586">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6587">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6587">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6588">Номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6588">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6589">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6589">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6590">Код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6590">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6591">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6591">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6592">пространство или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6592">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6593">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6593">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6594">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6594">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6595">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6595">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6596">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6596">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6597">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6597">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6598">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6598">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6599">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6599">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6600">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6600">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6601">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6601">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6602">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6602">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6603">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6603">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6604">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6604">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6605">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6605">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6652">Номер водительских прав в Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6652">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6653">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6653">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6654">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6654">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6655">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6655">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6656">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6656">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6657">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6657">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6658">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6658">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6659">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6659">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6660">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6660">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6661">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6661">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6662">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6662">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6692">運転免許証 Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6692">運転免許証No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6693">運転免許 Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6693">運転免許No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6694">免許証 Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6694">免許証No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6695">免許 Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6695">免許No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6696">運転免許証 #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6696">運転免許証#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6697">運転免許 #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6697">運転免許#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6698">免許証 #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6698">免許証#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6699">免許 #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6699">免許#</span></span>


## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6700">Япония Мой номер — корпоративная</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6700">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6701">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6701">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6702">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6702">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6703">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6703">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6704">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6704">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6705">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6705">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6706">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6706">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6707">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6707">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6708">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6708">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6709">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6709">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6710">13-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6710">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6711">одна цифра от одной до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6711">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6712">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6712">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6713">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6713">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6714">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6714">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6715">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6715">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6716">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6716">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6717">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6717">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6718">Ключевое слово Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6718">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6719">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6719">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6720">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6720">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6721">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6721">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_japan_my_number_corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6722">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6722">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6723">корпоративный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6723">corporate number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6724">マイナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6724">マイナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6725">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6725">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6726">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6726">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6727">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6727">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6728">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6728">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6729">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6729">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6730">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6730">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6731">法人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6731">法人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6732">指定通知書</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6732">指定通知書</span></span>


## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6733">Япония Мой номер - Личный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6733">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6734">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6734">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6735">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6735">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6736">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6736">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6737">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6737">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6738">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6738">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6739">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6739">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6740">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6740">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6741">12-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6741">12-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6742">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6742">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6743">12-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6743">12-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6744">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6744">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6745">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6745">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6746">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6746">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6747">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6747">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6748">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6748">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6749">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6749">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6750">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6750">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6751">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6751">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6752">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6752">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6753">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6753">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6754">Ключевое слово Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6754">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6755">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6755">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6756">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6756">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6757">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6757">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_japan_my_number_personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6758">Keyword_japan_my_number_personal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6758">Keyword_japan_my_number_personal</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6759">мой номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6759">my number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6760">マイナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6760">マイナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6761">個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6761">個人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6762">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6762">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6763">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6763">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6764">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6764">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6765">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6765">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6766">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6766">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6767">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6767">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6768">通知カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6768">通知カード</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6769">Номер паспорта Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6769">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6770">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6770">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6771">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6771">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6772">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6772">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6773">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу), за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6773">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6774">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6774">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6775">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6775">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6776">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6776">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6777">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6777">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6778">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6778">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6779">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6779">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6780">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6780">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6781">Keyword_jp_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6781">Keyword_jp_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6782">Паспорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6782">Passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6783">Passport Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6783">Passport Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6784">Паспорт No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6784">Passport No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6785">Passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6785">Passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6786">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6786">パスポート</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6787">パスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6787">パスポート番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6788">パスポートナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6788">パスポートナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6789">パスポート＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6789">パスポート＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6790">パスポート #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6790">パスポート#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6791">パポ.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6791">パスポートNo.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6792">旅券番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6792">旅券番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6793">旅券番号＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6793">旅券番号＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6794">旅券番号♯</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6794">旅券番号♯</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6795">旅券ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6795">旅券ナンバー</span></span>


## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6796">Номер карты проживания в Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6796">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6797">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6797">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6798">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6798">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6799">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6799">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6800">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6800">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6801">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6801">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6802">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6802">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6803">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6803">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6804">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6804">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6805">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6805">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6806">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6806">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6807">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6807">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6808">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6808">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6809">Ключевое слово Keyword_jp_residence_card_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6809">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6810">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6810">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6811">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6811">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6812">Номер карточки residence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6812">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6813">Карточка residence no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6813">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6814">Карточка residence #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6814">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6815">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6815">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6816">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6816">在留カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6817">在留番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6817">在留番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6818">Регистрационный номер резидента Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6818">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6819">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6819">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6820">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6820">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6821">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6821">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6822">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6822">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6823">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6823">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6824">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6824">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6825">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6825">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6826">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6826">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6827">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6827">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6828">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6828">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6829">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6829">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_resident_registration_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6830">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6830">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6831">Resident Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6831">Resident Registration Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6832">Residents Basic Registry Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6832">Residents Basic Registry Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6833">Resident Registration No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6833">Resident Registration No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6834">Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6834">Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6835">Residents Basic Registry No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6835">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6836">Basic Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6836">Basic Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6837">外国人登録証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6837">外国人登録証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6838">証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6838">証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6839">登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6839">登録番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6840">外国人登録証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6840">外国人登録証</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6841">Номер социального страхования Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6841">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6842">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6842">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6843">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6843">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6844">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6844">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6845">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6845">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6846">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6846">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6847">дефис (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6847">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6848">шесть цифр OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6848">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6849">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6849">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6850">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6850">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6851">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6851">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6852">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6852">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6853">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6853">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6854">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6854">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6855">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6855">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6856">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6856">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6857">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6857">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6858">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6858">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6859">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6859">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6860">Keyword_jp_sin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6860">Keyword_jp_sin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6861">Social Insurance No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6861">Social Insurance No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6862">Social Insurance Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6862">Social Insurance Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6863">Social Insurance Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6863">Social Insurance Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6864">健康保険被保険者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6864">健康保険被保険者番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6865">健保番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6865">健保番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6866">基礎年金番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6866">基礎年金番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6867">雇用保険被保険者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6867">雇用保険被保険者番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6868">雇用保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6868">雇用保険番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6869">保険証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6869">保険証番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6870">社会保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6870">社会保険番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6871">社会保険 Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6871">社会保険No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6872">社会保険</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6872">社会保険</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6873">介護保険</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6873">介護保険</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6874">介護保険被保険者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6874">介護保険被保険者番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6875">健康保険被保険者整理番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6875">健康保険被保険者整理番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6876">雇用保険被保険者整理番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6876">雇用保険被保険者整理番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6877">厚生年金</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6877">厚生年金</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6878">厚生年金被保険者整理番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6878">厚生年金被保険者整理番号</span></span>


## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6879">Номер водительских прав в Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6879">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6880">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6880">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6881">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6881">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6882">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6882">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6883">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6883">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6884">три буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6884">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6885">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6885">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6886">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6886">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6887">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6887">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6888">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6888">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6889">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6889">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6890">Обычное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6890">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-6891">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-6891">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
```

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7018">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7018">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7019">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7019">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7020">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7020">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7021">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7021">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7022">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (DDMMYY)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7022">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7023">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7023">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7024">одна цифра, соответствующая столетию рождения ("0" для 19-го века, "1" для 20-го века и "2" для 21-го века)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7024">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7025">четыре цифры, случайно созданные</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7025">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7026">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7026">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7027">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7027">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7028">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7028">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7029">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7029">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7030">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7030">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7031">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7031">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7032">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7032">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7033">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7033">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7034">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7034">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7035">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7035">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7036">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7036">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7037">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7037">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7100">Номер паспорта Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7100">Latvia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7101">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7101">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7102">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7102">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7103">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7103">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7104">две буквы или цифры, а затем семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7104">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7105">две цифры или буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7105">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7106">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7106">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7107">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7107">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7108">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7108">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7109">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7109">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7110">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7110">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7111">Обычное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7111">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7112">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7112">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7113">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7113">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7114">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7114">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7115">Обычное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7115">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7116">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7116">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="23ae25ec-cc28-421b-b77a-3054eadf1ede" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7139">Номер водительских прав Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7139">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7140">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7140">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7141">восемь цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7141">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7142">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7142">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7143">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7143">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7144">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7144">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7145">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7145">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7146">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7146">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7147">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7147">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7148">Обычное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7148">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7149">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7149">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7274">Личный код Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7274">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7275">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7275">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7276">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7276">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7277">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7277">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7278">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7278">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7279">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7279">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7280">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7280">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7281">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7281">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7282">11 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7282">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7283">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7283">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7284">11 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7284">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7285">одна цифра (1-6), соответствующая полу и столетию рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7285">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7286">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7286">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7287">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру даты рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7287">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7288">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7288">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7289">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7289">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7290">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7290">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7291">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7291">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7292">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7292">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7293">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7293">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7294">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7294">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7295">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7295">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7296">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7296">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7331">Номер паспорта Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7331">Lithuania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7332">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7332">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7333">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7333">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7334">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7334">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7335">восемь цифр или букв (не чувствительных к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7335">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7336">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7336">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7337">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7337">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7338">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7338">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7339">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7339">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7340">Обычное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7340">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7341">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7341">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7342">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате DD MM YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7342">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7343">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7343">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7344">Обычное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7344">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7345">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7345">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1b79900f-047b-4c3f-846f-7d73b5534bce" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7365">Номер водительских прав в Люксембурге</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7365">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7366">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7366">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7367">шесть цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7367">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7368">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7368">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7369">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7369">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7370">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7370">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7371">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7371">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7372">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7372">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7373">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7373">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7374">Обычное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7374">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7375">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7375">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7499">Национальный идентификационный номер Люксембурга (естественные лица)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7499">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7500">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7500">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7501">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7501">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7502">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7502">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7503">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7503">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7504">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7504">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7505">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7505">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7506">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7506">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7507">13 цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7507">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7508">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7508">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7509">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7509">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7510">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7510">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7511">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7511">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7512">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7512">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7513">да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7513">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7514">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7514">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7515">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7515">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7516">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7516">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7517">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7517">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7518">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7518">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7519">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7519">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
