## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7542">Номер паспорта Люксембурга</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7542">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7543">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7543">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7544">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7544">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7545">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7545">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7546">восемь цифр или букв (не чувствительных к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7546">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7547">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7547">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7548">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7548">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7549">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7549">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7550">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7550">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7551">Обычное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7551">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7552">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7552">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7553">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате DD MM YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7553">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7554">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7554">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7555">Обычное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7555">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7556">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7556">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="81d5c027-bed9-4421-91a0-3b2e55b3eb85" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7588">Номер национальной идентификации в Люксембурге (не естественное лицо)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7588">Luxemburg national identification number (non-natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7589">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7589">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7590">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7590">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7591">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7591">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7592">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7592">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7593">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7593">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7594">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7594">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7595">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7595">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7596">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7596">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7597">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7597">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7598">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7598">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7599">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7599">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7600">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7600">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7601">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7601">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7602">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7602">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7603">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7603">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7604">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7604">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7605">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7605">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7606">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7606">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7607">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7607">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7608">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7608">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7648">Номер удостоверения личности Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7648">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7649">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7649">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7650">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные дефисы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7650">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7651">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7651">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7652">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7652">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7653">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7653">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7654">тире (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7654">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7655">двух-буквный код места рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7655">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7656">тире (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7656">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7657">три случайных цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7657">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7658">однозначный гендерный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7658">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7659">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7659">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7660">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7660">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7661">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7661">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7662">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7662">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7663">регулярное выражение Regex_malaysia_id_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7663">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7664">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7664">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7691">Номер водительского удостоверения Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7691">Malta driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7692">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7692">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7693">Сочетание двух символов и шести цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7693">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7694">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7694">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7695">сочетание двух символов и шести цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7695">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7696">два символа (цифры или буквы, не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7696">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7697">пробел (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7697">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7698">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7698">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7699">пробел (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7699">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7700">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7700">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7701">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7701">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7702">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7702">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7703">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7703">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7704">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7704">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7705">Обычное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7705">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7706">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7706">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="a3bdaa4a-8371-4735-8fa5-56ee0fb4afc4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7830">Номер удостоверения личности Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7830">Malta identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7831">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7831">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7832">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7832">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7833">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7833">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7834">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7834">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7835">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7835">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7836">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7836">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7837">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7837">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7838">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7838">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7839">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7839">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7840">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7840">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7841">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7841">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7842">одна буква в "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (случай нечувствительный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7842">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7843">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7843">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7844">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7844">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7845">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7845">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7846">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7846">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7847">Обычное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7847">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7848">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7848">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7849">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7849">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7850">Обычное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7850">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7852">Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7852">Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7853">номер службы гражданина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7853">citizen service number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7859">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7859">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7860">numru ta' identità uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7860">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7861">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7861">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7862">numru tat-taxxa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7862">numru tat-taxxa</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7866">uniqueidentityno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7866">uniqueidentityno#</span></span>


## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7867">Номер паспорта Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7867">Malta passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7868">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7868">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7869">семь цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7869">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7870">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7870">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7871">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7871">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7872">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7872">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7873">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7873">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7874">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7874">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7875">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7875">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7876">Обычное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7876">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7877">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7877">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7878">Найдено `Keywords_eu_passport_date` ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7878">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7879">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7879">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7880">Обычное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7880">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7881">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7881">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="b2b21198-48f9-4d13-b2a5-03969bff0fb8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7882">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7882">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7883">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7883">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7884">паспорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7884">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7885">паспорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7885">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7886">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7886">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7887">паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7887">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7888">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7888">passportno</span></span>

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7901">Номер идентификации налога На Мальте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7901">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7902">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7902">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7903">Для граждан Мальты:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7903">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7904">семь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7904">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7905">Не мальтийские граждане и мальтийские юридические лица:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7905">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7906">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7906">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7907">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7907">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7908">Граждане Мальты: семь цифр и одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7908">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7909">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7909">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7910">одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7910">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7911">Не мальтийские граждане и мальтийские сущностями: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7911">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7912">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7912">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7913">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7913">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7914">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7914">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7915">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7915">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7916">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7916">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7917">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7917">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7918">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7918">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7919">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7919">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7920">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7920">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7921">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7921">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7922">Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7922">Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7926">kodiċi цифры personali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7926">kodiċi numerali personali</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7930">numru ta' identità uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7930">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7931">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7931">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7932">numru tat-taxxa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7932">numru tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7933">личный числимый код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7933">personal numeric code</span></span>

## <a name="medicare-beneficiary-identifier-mbi-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7953">Идентификатор бенефициара Medicare (MBI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7953">Medicare Beneficiary Identifier (MBI) card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7954">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7954">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7955">одиннадцати символов альфа-числовом шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7955">eleven character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7956">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7956">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7957">одна цифра от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7957">one digit between 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7958">одна буква, за исключением S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7958">one letter excluding  S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7959">одна цифра или буква, за исключением S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7959">one digit or letter excluding S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7960">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7960">one digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7961">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7961">an optional Hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7962">одна буква, за исключением S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7962">one letter excluding  S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7963">одна цифра или буква, за исключением S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7963">one digit or letter excluding S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7964">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7964">one digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7965">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7965">an optional Hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7966">две буквы, за исключением S, L, O, I, B, Z</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7966">two letters excluding  S, L, O, I, B, Z</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7967">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7967">two digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7968">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7968">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7969">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7969">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7970">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7970">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7971">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7971">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7972">Обычное выражение  `Regex_mbi_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7972">The regular expression  `Regex_mbi_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7973">Найдено ключевое  `Keyword_mbi_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7973">A keyword from  `Keyword_mbi_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7974">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7974">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7975">Обычное выражение  `Regex_mbi_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7975">The regular expression  `Regex_mbi_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
    <!-- Medicare Beneficiary Identifier (MBI) card -->
      <Entity id="f753a286-f5cc-47e6-a592-4be25fd02591" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_mbi_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_mbi_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_mbi_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7976">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7976">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_mbi_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7977">Keyword_mbi_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7977">Keyword_mbi_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7978">mbi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7978">mbi</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7979">mbi #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7979">mbi#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7980">получатель medicare #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7980">medicare beneficiary #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7981">идентификатор бенефициара medicare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7981">medicare beneficiary identifier</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7982">получателя medicare нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7982">medicare beneficiary no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7983">номер получателя medicare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7983">medicare beneficiary number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7984">получатель medicare #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7984">medicare beneficiary#</span></span>


## <a name="mexico-unique-population-registry-code-curp"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7985">Код реестра уникальных популяций Мексики (CURP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7985">Mexico Unique Population Registry Code (CURP)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7986">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7986">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7987">Альфанумерный шаблон 18 символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7987">18 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7988">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7988">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7989">четыре буквы (случай нечувствительный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7989">four letters (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7990">шесть цифр с указанием допустимой даты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7990">six digits indicating a valid date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7991">письмо - H/h или M/m</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7991">a letter - H/h or M/m</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7992">два буквы, указывающие допустимый мексиканский код состояния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7992">two letters indicating a valid Mexican state code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7993">три буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7993">three letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7994">одна буква или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7994">one letter or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7995">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7995">one digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7996">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7996">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7997">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7997">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7998">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7998">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-7999">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-7999">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8000">Функция находит  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8000">The function  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8001">Найдено ключевое  `Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8001">A keyword from  `Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8002">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8002">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8003">Функция находит  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8003">The function  `Func_mexico_population_registry_code` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
    <!-- Mexico Unique Population Registry Code (CURP) -->
      <Entity id="e905ad4d-5a74-406d-bf36-b1efca798af4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_mexico_population_registry_code" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_mexico_population_registry_code" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8004">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8004">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_mexico_population_registry_code"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8005">Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8005">Keyword_mexico_population_registry_code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8007">Clave Unica de Registro de Poblacion</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8007">Clave Unica de Registro de Poblacion</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8008">Уникальный код реестра населения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8008">Unique Population Registry Code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8009">уникальный код населения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8009">unique population code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8010">CURP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8010">CURP</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8011">Личный ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8011">Personal ID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8012">Уникальный ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8012">Unique ID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8013">personalid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8013">personalid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8014">personalidnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8014">personalidnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8015">uniqueidkey</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8015">uniqueidkey</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8016">uniqueidnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8016">uniqueidnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8017">clave única</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8017">clave única</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8023">clavepersonalIdentidad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8023">clavepersonalIdentidad</span></span>


## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8024">Номер службы гражданина Нидерландов (BSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8024">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8025">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8025">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8026">восемь или девять цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8026">eight or nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8027">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8027">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8028">восемь-девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8028">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8029">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8029">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8030">пробел (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8030">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8031">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8031">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8032">пробел (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8032">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8033">две-три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8033">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8034">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8034">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8035">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8035">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8036">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8036">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8037">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8037">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8038">функция Func_netherlands_bsn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8038">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8039">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_netherlands_bsn;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8039">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8040">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8040">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8050">номер, связанный с человеком</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8050">person-related number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8051">persoonlijk nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8051">persoonlijk nummer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8056">социально-финансовый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8056">social-fiscal number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8057">sofi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8057">sofi</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8059">uniek identificatienummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8059">uniek identificatienummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8060">uniek identiteitsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8060">uniek identiteitsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8061">уникальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8061">unique identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8062">уникальный номер удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8062">unique identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8063">uniqueidentityno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8063">uniqueidentityno#</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8064">Номер водительских прав Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8064">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8065">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8065">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8066">десять цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8066">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8067">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8067">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8068">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8068">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8069">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8069">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8070">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8070">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8071">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8071">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8072">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8072">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8073">Обычное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8073">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8074">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8074">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="6247fbea-ab80-4be5-8233-308b7c031401" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8075">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8075">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8084">lics драйвера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8084">driver lics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8085">driver license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8085">driver license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8086">driver licenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8086">driver licenses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8087">водительское удостоверение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8087">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8088">водительские права</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8088">driver licences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8089">driverslic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8089">driverslic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8090">driverslics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8090">driverslics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8091">driverslicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8091">driverslicence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8092">driverslicences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8092">driverslicences</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8202">Номер паспорта Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8202">Netherlands passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8203">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8203">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8204">девять букв или цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8204">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8205">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8205">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8206">девять букв или цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8206">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8207">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8207">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8208">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8208">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8209">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8209">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8210">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8210">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8211">Обычное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8211">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8212">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8212">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8213">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Пример - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8213">The regular expression `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8214">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8214">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8215">Обычное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8215">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8216">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8216">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61786727-bafd-45f6-94d9-888d815e228e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8230">nummer paspoort</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8230">paspoort nummer</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8234">Номер налоговой идентификации в Нидерландах</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8234">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8235">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8235">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8236">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8236">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8237">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8237">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8238">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8238">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8239">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8239">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8240">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8240">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8241">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8241">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8242">девять цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8242">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8243">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8243">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8244">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8244">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8245">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8245">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8246">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8246">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8247">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8247">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8248">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8248">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8249">Функция находит  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8249">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8250">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8250">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8251">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8251">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8252">Функция находит  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8252">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8290">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Нидерландах</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8290">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8291">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8291">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8292">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8292">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8293">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8293">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8294">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8294">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8295">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8295">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8296">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8296">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8297">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8297">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8298">Альфанумерный шаблон 14 символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8298">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8299">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8299">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8300">14-символический альфанумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8300">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8301">N или n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8301">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8302">L или l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8302">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8303">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8303">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8304">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8304">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8305">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8305">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8306">B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8306">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8307">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8307">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8308">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8308">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8309">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8309">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8310">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8310">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8311">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8311">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8312">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8312">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8313">Найдено ключевое слово Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8313">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8314">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8314">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8315">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8315">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8324">Номер банковского счета в Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8324">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8325">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8325">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8326">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8326">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8327">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8327">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8328">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8328">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8329">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8329">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8330">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8330">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8331">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8331">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8332">14-значный и 16-значный шаблон с необязательным делимитером</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8332">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8333">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8333">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8334">14-значный и 16-значный шаблон с необязательным делимитером:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8334">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8335">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8335">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8336">необязательный дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8336">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8337">три-четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8337">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8338">необязательный дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8338">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8339">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8339">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8340">необязательный дефис или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8340">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8341">две-три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8341">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8342">дефис параметров или пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8342">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8343">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8343">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8344">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8344">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8345">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8345">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8346">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8346">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8347">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8347">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8348">Ключевое слово Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8348">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8349">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8349">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8350">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8350">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zFealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
