## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8358">Номер водительского удостоверения Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8358">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8359">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8359">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8360">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8360">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8361">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8361">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8362">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8362">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8363">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8363">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8364">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8364">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8365">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8365">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8366">восемь шаблонов альфа-цифр символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8366">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8367">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8367">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8368">восемь шаблонов альфа-цифр символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8368">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8369">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8369">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8370">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8370">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8371">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8371">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8372">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8372">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8373">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8373">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8374">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8374">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8375">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8375">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8376">Ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8376">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8377">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8377">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8378">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8378">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8445">Число внутренних доходов Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8445">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8446">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8446">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8447">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8447">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8448">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8448">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8449">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8449">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8450">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8450">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8451">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8451">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8452">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8452">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8453">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делимитерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8453">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8454">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8454">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8455">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делимитерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8455">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8456">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8456">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8457">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8457">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8458">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8458">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8459">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8459">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8460">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8460">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8461">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8461">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8462">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8462">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8463">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8463">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8464">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8464">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8465">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8465">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8466">Ключевое слово Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8466">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8467">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8467">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8468">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8468">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8469">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8469">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8470">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8470">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8471">ird Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8471">ird no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8472">ird no #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8472">ird no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8473">nz ird</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8473">nz ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8474">ird Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8474">new zealand ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8475">ird number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8475">ird number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8476">число внутренних доходов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8476">inland revenue number</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8477">Номер министерства здравоохранения Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8477">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8478">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8478">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8479">три буквы, пространство (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8479">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8480">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8480">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8481">три буквы (не чувствительные к делу), кроме "I" и "O"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8481">three letters (not case-sensitive) except 'I' and 'O'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8482">пробел (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8482">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8483">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8483">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8484">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8484">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8485">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8485">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8486">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8486">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8487">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8487">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8488">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8488">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8489">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8489">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8490">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8490">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8491">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8491">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8492">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8492">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8493">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8493">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
    <Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
       </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8494">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8494">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_nz_terms"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8495">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8495">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8496">NHI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8496">NHI</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8499">обработка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8499">treatment</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8500">Номер национального индекса здоровья</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8500">National Health Index Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8501">nhi number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8501">nhi number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8502">nhi нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8502">nhi no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8503">NHI #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8503">NHI#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8504">Национальный индекс здоровья No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8504">National Health Index No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8505">Национальный индекс здоровья</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8505">National Health Index Id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8506">Национальный индекс здоровья #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8506">National Health Index #</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-social-welfare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8507">Номер социального обеспечения в Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8507">New Zealand social welfare number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8508">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8508">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8509">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8509">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8510">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8510">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8511">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8511">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8512">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8512">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8513">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8513">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8514">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8514">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8515">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8515">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8516">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8516">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8517">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8517">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8518">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8518">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8519">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8519">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8520">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8520">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8521">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8521">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8522">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8522">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8523">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8523">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8524">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8524">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8525">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8525">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8526">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8526">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8527">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8527">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8528">Ключевое слово Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8528">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8529">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8529">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8530">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8530">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8531">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8531">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8532">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8532">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8533">социальное обеспечение #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8533">social welfare #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8534">социальное обеспечение #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8534">social welfare#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8535">No социального обеспечения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8535">social welfare No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8536">номер социального обеспечения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8536">social welfare number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8537">swn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8537">swn#</span></span>

   
## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8538">Идентификационный номер Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8538">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8539">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8539">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8540">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8540">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8541">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8541">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8542">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8542">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8543">шесть цифр в формате DDMMYY, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8543">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8544">трехзначный индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8544">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8545">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8545">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8546">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8546">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8547">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8547">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8548">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8548">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8549">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8549">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8550">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8550">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8551">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8551">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8552">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8552">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8553">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8553">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8554">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8554">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8555">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8555">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8556">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8556">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_norway_id_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8557">Keyword_norway_id_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8557">Keyword_norway_id_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8558">Personal identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8558">Personal identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8559">Norwegian ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8559">Norwegian ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8560">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8560">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8561">Идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8561">Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8562">Personnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8562">Personnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8563">Fødselsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8563">Fødselsnummer</span></span>

   
## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8564">Филиппины единый многоцелевой идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8564">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8565">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8565">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8566">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8566">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8567">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8567">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8568">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8568">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8569">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8569">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8570">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8570">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8571">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8571">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8572">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8572">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8573">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8573">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8574">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8574">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8575">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8575">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8576">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8576">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8577">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8577">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8578">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8578">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8579">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8579">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8580">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8580">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8581">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8581">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8582">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8582">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8583">UMID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8583">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8584">Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8584">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8585">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8585">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8586">Номер водительских прав в Польше</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8586">Poland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8587">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8587">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8588">14 цифр, содержащих две косые черты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8588">14 digits containing two forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8589">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8589">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8590">14 цифр и две косые черты:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8590">14 digits and two forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8591">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8591">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8592">перенарезаемая косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8592">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8593">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8593">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8594">перенарезаемая косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8594">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8595">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8595">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8596">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8596">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8597">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8597">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8598">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8598">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8599">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8599">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8600">Обычное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8600">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8601">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8601">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8602">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8602">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8604">driverlic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8604">driverlic</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8607">driverlicenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8607">driverlicenses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8608">driverlicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8608">driverlicence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8609">driverlicences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8609">driverlicences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8610">lic драйвера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8610">driver lic</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8613">driver licenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8613">driver licenses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8614">водительское удостоверение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8614">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8615">водительские права</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8615">driver licences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8616">driverslic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8616">driverslic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8617">driverslics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8617">driverslics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8618">driverslicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8618">driverslicence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8619">driverslicences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8619">driverslicences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8620">driverslicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8620">driverslicense</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8621">driverslicenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8621">driverslicenses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8622">драйверы lic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8622">drivers lic</span></span>

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8725">Удостоверение личности в Польше</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8725">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8726">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8726">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8727">три буквы и шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8727">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8728">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8728">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8729">три буквы (не чувствительные к делу) с последующим шестью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8729">three letters (not case-sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8730">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8730">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8731">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8731">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8732">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8732">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8733">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8733">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8734">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8734">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8735">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8735">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8736">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8736">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8747">Польский национальный ID (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8747">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8748">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8748">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8749">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8749">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8750">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8750">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8751">шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения в формате YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8751">six digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8752">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8752">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8753">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8753">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8754">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8754">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8755">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8755">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8756">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8756">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8757">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8757">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8758">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8758">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8759">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8759">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8760">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8760">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8761">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8761">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8762">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8762">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8763">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8763">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8764">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8764">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_pesel_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8765">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8765">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8766">dowód osobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8766">dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8767">dowódosobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8767">dowódosobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8768">niepowtarzalny numer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8768">niepowtarzalny numer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8769">niepowtarzalnynumer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8769">niepowtarzalnynumer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8770">nr.-pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8770">nr.-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8771">nr-pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8771">nr-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8772">numer identyfikacyjny</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8772">numer identyfikacyjny</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8773">pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8773">pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8774">tożsamości narodowej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8774">tożsamości narodowej</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8775">Номер паспорта Польши</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8775">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8776">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации входит в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8776">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8777">Он доступен в виде отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8777">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8778">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8778">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8779">две буквы и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8779">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8780">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8780">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8781">Две буквы (не чувствительные к делу) с семью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8781">Two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8782">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8782">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8783">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8783">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8784">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8784">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8785">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8785">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8786">Функция находит `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8786">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8787">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8787">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8788">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8788">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8789">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_eu_passport_date` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8789">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8790">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8790">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8791">Функция находит `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8791">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8792">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8792">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8793">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8793">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8794">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8794">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8795">Функция находит `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8795">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8796">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8796">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8797">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8797">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8798">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8798">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8801">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8801">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8802">паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8802">passports</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8806">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8806">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8807">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8807">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8808">номера паспортов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8808">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_polish_national_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8809">Keyword_polish_national_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8809">Keyword_polish_national_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8810">numer paszportu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8810">numer paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8811">numery paszportów</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8811">numery paszportów</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8812">numery paszportowe</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8812">numery paszportowe</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8813">nr paszportu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8813">nr paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8814">nr.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8814">nr.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8815">paszportu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8815">paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8816">nr paszportów</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8816">nr paszportów</span></span>

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8822">Номер REGON в Польше</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8822">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8823">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8823">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8824">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8824">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8825">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8825">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8826">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8826">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8827">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8827">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8828">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8828">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8829">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8829">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8830">9-значный или 14-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8830">9-digit or 14-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8831">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8831">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8832">девять цифр или 14-значное число:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8832">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8833">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8833">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8834">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8834">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8835">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8835">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8836">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8836">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8837">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8837">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8838">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8838">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8839">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8839">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8840">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8840">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8841">Функция Func_polish_regon_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8841">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8842">Ключевое слово Keywords_polish_regon_number найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8842">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8843">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8843">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8844">Функция Func_polish_regon_number контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8844">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8849">статистический id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8849">statistical id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8850">статистический нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8850">statistical no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8851">номер regon</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8851">regon number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8852">regonid #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8852">regonid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8853">regonno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8853">regonno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8854">ID компании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8854">company id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8855">companyid #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8855">companyid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8856">companyidno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8856">companyidno#</span></span>

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8861">Номер налоговой идентификации в Польше</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8861">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8862">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8862">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8863">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8863">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8864">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8864">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8865">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8865">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8866">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8866">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8867">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8867">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8868">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8868">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8869">11 цифр без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8869">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8870">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8870">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8871">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8871">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8872">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8872">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8873">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8873">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8874">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8874">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8875">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8875">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8876">Функция находит  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8876">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8877">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8877">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8907">Номер карточки гражданина Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8907">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8908">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8908">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8909">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8909">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8910">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8910">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8911">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8911">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8912">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8912">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8913">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8913">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8914">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8914">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8915">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8915">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8916">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8916">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8917">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8917">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8924">documento de identificação</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8924">documento de identificação</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8933">número de identificação civil</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8933">número de identificação civil</span></span>

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8937">Номер водительских прав Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8937">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8938">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8938">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8939">два шаблона : две буквы с 5-8 цифрами со специальными символами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8939">two patterns - two letters followed by 5-8 digits with special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8940">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8940">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8941">Шаблон 1. Две буквы, за которыми следуют 5/6 со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8941">Pattern 1: Two letters followed by 5/6 with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8942">Две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8942">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8943">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8943">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8944">Пять или шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8944">Five or Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8945">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8945">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8946">Одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8946">One digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8947">Шаблон 2. Одна буква с 6/8 цифрами со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8947">Pattern 2: One letter followed by 6/8 digits with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8948">Одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8948">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8949">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8949">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8950">Шесть или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8950">Six or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8951">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8951">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8952">одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8952">One digit</span></span>

    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8953">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8953">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8954">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8954">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8955">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8955">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8956">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8956">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8957">Обычное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8957">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-8958">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-8958">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="977f1e5a-2c33-4bcc-b516-95bb275cff23" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9090">Номер паспорта Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9090">Portugal passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9091">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9091">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9092">одна буква с шестью цифрами без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9092">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9093">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9093">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9094">одна буква с шестью цифрами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9094">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9095">одна буква (не деликатная)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9095">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9096">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9096">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9097">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9097">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9098">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9098">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9099">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9099">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9100">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9100">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9101">Обычное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9101">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9102">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9102">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9103">Обычное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате DD.MM.YYYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9103">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9104">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9104">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9105">Обычное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9105">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9106">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9106">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="080a52fd-a7bc-431e-b54d-51f08f59db11" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-9107">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-9107">Keywords</span></span>
