## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10050">Идентификационный номер Южной Африки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10050">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10051">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10051">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10052">13 цифр, которые могут содержать пробелы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10052">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10053">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10053">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10054">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10054">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10055">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10055">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10056">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10056">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10057">однозначный индикатор гражданства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10057">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10058">цифры "8" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10058">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10059">одна цифра, которая является цифрой чека</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10059">one digit, which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10060">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10060">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10061">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10061">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10062">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10062">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10063">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10063">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10064">функция Func_south_africa_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10064">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10065">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_africa_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10065">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10066">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10066">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10067">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10067">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_africa_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10068">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10068">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10069">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10069">Identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10070">ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10070">ID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10071">Идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10071">Identification</span></span> 
   
## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10072">Номер регистрации резидента Южной Кореи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10072">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10073">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10073">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10074">13 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10074">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10075">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10075">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10076">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10076">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10077">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10077">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10078">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10078">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10079">одна цифра, определяемая веком и полом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10079">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10080">четырехзначный код региона рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10080">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10081">одна цифра, используемая для дифференцировки людей, для которых предыдущие номера идентичны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10081">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10082">контрольная цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10082">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10083">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10083">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10084">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10084">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10085">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10085">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10086">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10086">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10087">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10087">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10088">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_korea_resident_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10088">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10089">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10089">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10090">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10090">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10091">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10091">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10092">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10092">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10093">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10093">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10094">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10094">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10095">National ID card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10095">National ID card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10096">Citizen's Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10096">Citizen's Registration Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10097">Jumin deungnok beonho</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10097">Jumin deungnok beonho</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10098">RRN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10098">RRN</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10099">주민등록번호</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10099">주민등록번호</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10100">Номер водительских прав Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10100">Spain driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10101">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10101">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10102">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10102">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10103">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10103">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10104">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10104">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10105">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10105">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10106">одна цифра или буква (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10106">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10107">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10107">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10108">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10108">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10109">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10109">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10110">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10110">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10111">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` поиск контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10111">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10112">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10112">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10113">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10113">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10114">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` поиск контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10114">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5a82922-b501-4f40-8868-341321146aa2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-dni"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10248">DNI Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10248">Spain DNI</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10249">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10249">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10250">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10250">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10251">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10251">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10252">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10252">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10253">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10253">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10254">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10254">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10255">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10255">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10256">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10256">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10257">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10257">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10258">семь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10258">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10259">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10259">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10260">Необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10260">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10261">одно чековая буква (не чувствительное к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10261">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10262">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10262">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10263">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10263">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10264">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10264">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10265">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10265">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10266">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` поиск контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10266">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10267">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10267">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10268">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10268">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10269">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` поиск контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10269">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

    
```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10293">Номер паспорта Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10293">Spain passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10294">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10294">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10295">сочетание букв и номеров с восемью или девятью символами без пробелов или делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10295">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10296">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10296">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10297">сочетание букв и номеров с восемью или девятью символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10297">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10298">две цифры или буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10298">two digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10299">одна цифра или буква (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10299">one digit or letter (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10300">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10300">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10301">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10301">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10302">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10302">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10303">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10303">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10304">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10304">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10305">Обычное выражение  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10305">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10306">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10306">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10307">Регулярное выражение `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` находит дату в формате DD-MM-YYYYY или найдено ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10307">The regular expression `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD-MM-YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10308">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10308">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10309">Обычное выражение  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10309">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10310">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10310">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d17a57de-9fa5-4e9f-85d3-85c26d89686e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10339">Номер социального обеспечения Испании (SSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10339">Spain social security number (SSN)</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10340">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10340">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10341">11–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10341">11-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10342">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10342">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10343">11-12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10343">11-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10344">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10344">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10345">косая черта (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10345">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10346">семь-восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10346">seven to eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10347">косая черта (необязательный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10347">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10348">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10348">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10349">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10349">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10350">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10350">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10351">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10351">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10352">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10352">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10353">функция Func_spanish_social_security_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10353">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10354">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10354">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10355">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10355">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10356">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10356">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10357">функция Func_spanish_social_security_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10357">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10358">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10358">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Spain SSN -->
    <Entity id="5df987c0-8eae-4bce-ace7-b316347f3070" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10359">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10359">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_spain_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10360">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10360">Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="spain-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10367">Идентификация налога в Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10367">Spain tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10368">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10368">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10369">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10369">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10370">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10370">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10371">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10371">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10372">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10372">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10373">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10373">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10374">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10374">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10375">семь или восемь цифр и одна или две буквы в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10375">seven or eight digits and one or two letters in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10376">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10376">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10377">Испанские граждане с национальным удостоверением личности Испании:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10377">Spanish Natural Persons with a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10378">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10378">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10379">одно верхнее письмо (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10379">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10380">Испанцы-нерезиденты без национального удостоверения личности Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10380">Non-resident Spaniards without a Spain National Identity Card</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10381">одно верхнее письмо "L" (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10381">one uppercase letter "L" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10382">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10382">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10383">одно верхнее письмо (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10383">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10384">Resident Spaniards under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10384">Resident Spaniards under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10385">одно верхнее письмо "K" (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10385">one uppercase letter "K" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10386">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10386">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10387">одно верхнее письмо (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10387">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10388">Иностранцы с идентификационным номером иностранца</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10388">Foreigners with a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10389">одно верхнее письмо с буквами "X", "Y" или "Z" (чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10389">one uppercase letter that is "X", "Y", or "Z" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10390">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10390">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10391">одно верхнее письмо (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10391">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10392">Иностранцы без идентификации иностранца</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10392">Foreigners without a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10393">одно верхнее письмо с буквой "M" (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10393">one uppercase letter that is "M" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10394">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10394">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10395">одно верхнее письмо (чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10395">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10396">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10396">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10397">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10397">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10398">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10398">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10399">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10399">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10400">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` поиск контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10400">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10401">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10401">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10402">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10402">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10403">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` поиск контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10403">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="10f0d113-b0e1-47dc-872a-a4f45b9376a3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sql-server-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10434">SQL Server подключения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10434">SQL Server connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10435">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10435">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10436">Строка "User Id", "User ID", "uid" или "UserId" с символами и строками, описанными в приведенной ниже схеме.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10436">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10437">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10437">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10438">строки "User Id", "User ID", "uid" или "UserId"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10438">the string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10439">любое сочетание между 1-200 буквами нижнего или верхнего шкафа, цифрами, символами, специальными символами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10439">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10440">строка "Пароль" или "pwd", где "pwd" не предшествует букве нижнего регистра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10440">the string "Password" or "pwd" where "pwd" isn't preceded by a lowercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10441">равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10441">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10442">любой символ, который не является символом доллара ($), процентным символом (%), больше символа (>), в символе (@), кавычках ("), зайколоне (;), левом скобке ([) или левой скобке ({)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10442">any character that isn't a dollar sign ($), percent symbol (%), greater than symbol (>), at symbol (@), quotation mark ("), semicolon (;), left brace([), or left bracket ({)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10443">любое сочетание из 7-128 символов, которые не являются полуколоном (;), слэшом (/) или кавычками ()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10443">any combination of 7-128 characters that are not a semicolon (;), forward slash (/), or quotation mark (")</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10444">полуколон (;) или кавычка ()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10444">a semicolon (;) or quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10445">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10445">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10446">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10446">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10447">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10447">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10448">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10448">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10449">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10449">The regular expression CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10450">Ключевое слово CEP_GlobalFilter не найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10450">A keyword from CEP_GlobalFilter isn't found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10451">Обычное выражение CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder не находит контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10451">The regular expression CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10452">Обычное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10452">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```sql
<!---SQL Server Connection String>
<Entity id="e76b6205-d3cb-46f2-bd63-c90153f2f97d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_GlobalFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10453">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10453">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_globalfilter"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10454">CEP_GlobalFilter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10454">CEP_GlobalFilter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10455">some-password</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10455">some-password</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10456">somepassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10456">somepassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10457">secretPassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10457">secretPassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10458">пример</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10458">sample</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_passwordplaceholder"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10459">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10459">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10460">(Обратите внимание, что технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации определяет эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10460">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10461">Пароль или pwd с 0-2 пробелами, равным знаком (=), пробелами 0-2 и звездочкой (\*) -OR-</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10461">Password or pwd followed by 0-2 spaces, an equal sign (=), 0-2 spaces, and an asterisk (\*) -OR-</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10462">Пароль или pwd, за которыми следуют:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10462">Password or pwd followed by:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10463">Равный знак (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10463">Equal sign (=)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10464">Меньше символа (<)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10464">Less than symbol (<)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10465">Любое сочетание 1-200 символов, которые являются буквами верхнего или нижнего регистра, цифрами, звездочкой (\*), дефисом (-), подчеркнув (_) или символом whitespace</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10465">Any combination of 1-200 characters that are upper- or lowercase letters, digits, an asterisk (\*), hyphen (-), underline (_), or whitespace character</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10466">Больше символа (>)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10466">Greater than symbol (>)</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10480">Номер водительских прав Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10480">Sweden driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10481">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10481">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10482">десять цифр, содержащих дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10482">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10483">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10483">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10484">десять цифр, содержащих дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10484">ten digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10485">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10485">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10486">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10486">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10487">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10487">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10488">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10488">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10489">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10489">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10490">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10490">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10491">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10491">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10492">Обычное выражение  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10492">The regular expression  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10493">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10493">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="70088720-90dd-47f5-805e-5525f3567391" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10626">Национальный ID Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10626">Sweden national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10627">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10627">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10628">10 или 12 цифр и дополнительный разделитель.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10628">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10629">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10629">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10630">10 или 12 цифр с необязательным разделителем</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10630">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10631">две цифры (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10631">two digits (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10632">Шесть цифр в формате даты ГГММДД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10632">Six digits in date format YYMMDD</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10633">delimiter из "-" или "+" (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10633">delimiter of "-" or "+" (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10634">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10634">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10635">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10635">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10636">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10636">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10637">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10637">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10638">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10638">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10639">Функция находит `Func_swedish_national_identifier` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10639">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10640">Найдено `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10640">A keyword from `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10641">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10641">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10642">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10642">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10643">Функция находит `Func_swedish_national_identifier` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10643">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10644">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10644">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden National ID -->
    <Entity id="f69aaf40-79be-4fac-8f05-fd1910d272c8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10663">Номер паспорта Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10663">Sweden passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10664">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10664">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10665">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10665">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10666">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10666">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10667">восемь последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10667">eight consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10668">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10668">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10669">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10669">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10670">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10670">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10671">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10671">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10672">регулярное выражение Regex_sweden_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10672">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10673">ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` или `Keyword_sweden_passport` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10673">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10674">обычное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YY (01 JAN/JAN 12) или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из найденного.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10674">the regular expression `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` finds a date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (01 JAN/JAN 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10675">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10675">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10676">регулярное выражение Regex_sweden_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10676">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10677">ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` или `Keyword_sweden_passport` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10677">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="ba4e7456-55a9-4d89-9140-c33673553526" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10678">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10678">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10713">Номер налоговой идентификации в Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10713">Sweden tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10714">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10714">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10715">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10715">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10716">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10716">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10717">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10717">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10718">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10718">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10719">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10719">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10720">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10720">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10721">10 цифр и символ в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10721">10 digits and a symbol in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10722">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10722">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10723">10 цифр и символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10723">10 digits and a symbol:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10724">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10724">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10725">знак плюс или минус</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10725">a plus sign or minus sign</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10726">три цифры, которые делают идентификационный номер уникальным, где:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10726">three digits that make the identification number unique where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10727">для номеров, выдавшихся до 1990 г., седьмая и восьмая цифры определяют округ родившихся или родившихся за</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10727">for numbers issued before 1990, the seventh and eighth digit identify the county of birth or foreign-born people</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10728">цифра в девятой позиции указывает пол по нечетным для мужчин или даже для женщин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10728">the digit in the ninth position indicates gender by either odd for male or even for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10729">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10729">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10730">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10730">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10731">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10731">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10732">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10732">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10733">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10733">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10734">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10734">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10735">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10735">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10736">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10736">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10737">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10737">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="139acba0-a5bc-4fbb-876d-f7a493ae8a40" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10763">Код SWIFT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10763">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10764">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10764">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10765">четыре буквы с последующим 5-31 буквами или цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10765">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10766">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10766">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10767">четыре буквы, за которыми следуют 5-31 буквы или цифры:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10767">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10768">банковский код с четырьмя буквами (не чувствительный к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10768">four-letter bank code (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10769">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10769">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10770">4–28 букв или цифр (основной номер банковского счета, BBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10770">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10771">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10771">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10772">от одной до трех букв или цифр (остальная часть BBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10772">one to three letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10773">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10773">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10774">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10774">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10775">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10775">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10776">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10776">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10777">регулярное выражение Regex_swift находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10777">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10778">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_swift.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10778">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10779">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10779">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10789">swift number #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10789">swift number #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10790">swift routing number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10790">swift routing number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10791">bic number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10791">bic number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10792">bic code</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10792">bic code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10793">bic#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10793">bic #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10794">bic #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10794">bic#</span></span>

## <a name="switzerland-ssn-ahv-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10815">Номер AHV SSN в Швейцарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10815">Switzerland SSN AHV number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10816">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10816">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10817">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10817">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10818">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10818">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10819">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10819">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10820">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10820">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10821">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10821">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10822">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10822">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10823">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10823">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10824">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10824">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10825">13-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10825">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10826">три цифры - 756</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10826">three digits - 756</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10827">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10827">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10828">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10828">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10829">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10829">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10830">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10830">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10831">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10831">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10832">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10832">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10833">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10833">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10834">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10834">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10835">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10835">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10836">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10836">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10837">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10837">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10838">Ключевое слово Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10838">A keyword from Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10839">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10839">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10840">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10840">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Swiss SSN AHV Number -->
      <Entity id="277cfa4b-6eaa-4a1b-9492-099dec849971" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10858">sozialversicherungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10858">sozialversicherungsnummer</span></span>
