- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10860">numéro de sécurité sociale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10860">numéro de sécurité sociale</span></span>

   
## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10861">Национальный идентификационный номер Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10861">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10862">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10862">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10863">одна буква (на английском языке) с девятью цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10863">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10864">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10864">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10865">одна буква (на английском языке), а затем девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10865">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10866">одна буква (на английском языке, а не на английском языке)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10866">one letter (in English, not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10867">цифры "1" или "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10867">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10868">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10868">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10869">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10869">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10870">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10870">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10871">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10871">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10872">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10872">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10873">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10873">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10874">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwanese_national_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10874">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10875">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10875">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10876">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10876">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10877">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10877">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10878">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10878">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
<Entity id="4C7BFC34-8DD1-421D-8FB7-6C6182C2AF03" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwanese_national_id" />
      </Pattern>
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
         <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
       </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10886">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10886">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10887">身分證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10887">身分證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10888">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10888">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10889">身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10889">身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10890">國民身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10890">國民身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10891">簽名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10891">簽名</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10892">蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10892">蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10893">簽名或蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10893">簽名或蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10894">簽章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10894">簽章</span></span>   
   
## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10895">Номер паспорта Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10895">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10896">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10896">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10897">биометрический номер паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10897">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10898">не биометрический номер паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10898">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10899">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10899">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10900">биометрический номер паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10900">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10901">символ "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10901">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10902">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10902">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10903">не биометрический номер паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10903">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10904">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10904">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10905">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10905">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10906">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10906">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10907">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10907">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10908">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10908">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10909">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10909">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10910">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10910">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10911">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10911">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10912">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10912">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10913">ROC passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10913">ROC passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10914">Passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10914">Passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10915">Passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10915">Passport no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10916">Passport Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10916">Passport Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10917">Passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10917">Passport #</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10918">护照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10918">护照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10919">中華民國護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10919">中華民國護照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10920">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10920">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span></span>
   
## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10921">Номер сертификата жителя Тайваня (ARC/TARC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10921">Taiwan-resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10922">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10922">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10923">10 букв и цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10923">10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10924">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10924">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10925">10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10925">10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10926">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10926">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10927">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10927">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10928">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10928">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10929">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10929">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10930">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10930">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10931">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10931">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10932">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10932">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10933">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10933">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10934">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10934">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10935">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10935">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10936">Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10936">Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10937">Resident Cert</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10937">Resident Cert</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10938">Resident Cert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10938">Resident Cert.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10939">Identification card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10939">Identification card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10940">Alien Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10940">Alien Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10941">ARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10941">ARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10942">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10942">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10943">TARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10943">TARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10944">居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10944">居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10945">外僑居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10945">外僑居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10946">台灣地區居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10946">台灣地區居留證</span></span> 

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10947">Код идентификации населения Таиланда</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10947">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10948">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10948">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10949">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10949">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10950">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10950">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10951">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10951">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10952">первая цифра не ноль или девять</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10952">first digit isn't zero or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10953">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10953">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10954">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10954">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10955">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10955">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10956">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10956">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10957">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10957">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10958">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10958">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10959">Ключевое слово Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10959">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10960">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10960">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10961">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10961">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10962">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10962">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_thai_citizen_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10963">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10963">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10964">Идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10964">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10965">Идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10965">Identification Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10966">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10966">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10967">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10967">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10968">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10968">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10969">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10969">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
  
## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10970">Турецкий национальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10970">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10971">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10971">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10972">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10972">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10973">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10973">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10974">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10974">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10975">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10975">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10976">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10976">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10977">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10977">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10978">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10978">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10979">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10979">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10980">Ключевое слово из Keyword_Turkish_National_Id найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10980">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10981">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10981">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10982">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id контента, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10982">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10983">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10983">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_turkish_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10984">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10984">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10985">TC Kimlik No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10985">TC Kimlik No</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10986">TC Kimlik numarası</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10986">TC Kimlik numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10987">Vatandaşlık numarası</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10987">Vatandaşlık numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10988">Vatandaşlık нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10988">Vatandaşlık no</span></span>

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10989">U.K.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10989">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10990">номер лицензии водителя</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10990">driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10991">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10991">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10992">Сочетание 18 букв и цифр в указанном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10992">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10993">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10993">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10994">18 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10994">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10995">Пять букв (не чувствительных к делу) или цифра "9" на месте буквы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10995">Five letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10996">Одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10996">One digit.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10997">Пять цифр в формате даты MMDDY для даты рождения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10997">Five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10998">Седьмой символ приумножен на 50, если драйвер женский; для экзамена, от 51 до 62 вместо 01 до 12.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10998">The seventh character is incremented by 50 if driver is female; for exampe, 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-10999">Две буквы (не чувствительные к делу) или цифра "9" на месте буквы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-10999">Two letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11000">Пять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11000">Five digits.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11001">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11001">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11002">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11002">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11003">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11003">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11004">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11004">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11005">Функция находит `Func_uk_drivers_license` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11005">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11006">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11006">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11007">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11007">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11008">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11008">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11009">Функция находит `Func_uk_drivers_license` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11009">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11010">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11010">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11131">U.K.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11131">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11132">номер списка выборов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11132">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11133">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11133">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11134">две буквы, за которыми следуют 1-4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11134">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11135">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11135">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11136">две буквы (не чувствительные к делу) с последующим 1-4 числами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11136">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11137">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11137">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11138">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11138">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11139">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11139">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11140">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11140">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11141">регулярное выражение Regex_uk_electoral находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11141">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11142">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_electoral.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11142">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11143">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11143">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11144">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11144">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11145">council nomination</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11145">council nomination</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11146">nomination form</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11146">nomination form</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11147">electoral register</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11147">electoral register</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11148">electoral roll</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11148">electoral roll</span></span>

   
## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11149">U.K.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11149">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11150">номер службы здравоохранения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11150">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11151">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11151">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11152">10–17 цифр, разделенных пробелами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11152">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11153">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11153">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11154">10-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11154">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11155">3 или 10 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11155">either 3 or 10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11156">пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11156">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11157">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11157">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11158">пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11158">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11159">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11159">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11160">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11160">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11161">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11161">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11162">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11162">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11163">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11163">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11164">Функция Func_uk_nhs_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11164">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11165">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11165">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11166">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11166">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11167">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number1;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11167">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11168">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11168">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11169">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11169">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11170">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11170">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11171">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11171">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11175">health authority</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11175">health authority</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number1"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11176">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11176">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11177">patient id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11177">patient id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11178">patient identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11178">patient identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11179">patient no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11179">patient no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11180">patient number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11180">patient number</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11181">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11181">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11182">GP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11182">GP</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11183">DOB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11183">DOB</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11184">D.O.B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11184">D.O.B</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11185">Date of Birth</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11185">Date of Birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11186">Birth Date</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11186">Birth Date</span></span> 
   
## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11187">U.K.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11187">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11188">номер национального страхования (NINO)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11188">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11189">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации входит в тип конфиденциальной информации о номере национальной идентификации ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11189">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11190">Он доступен в виде отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11190">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11191">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11191">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11192">семь символов или девять символов, разделенных пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11192">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11193">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11193">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11194">два возможных шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11194">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11195">две буквы (допустимые ННИ используют только определенные символы в этом префиксе, который этот шаблон проверяет; не является чувствительным к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11195">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11196">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11196">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11197">или "A", "B", "C", "D" (как и префикс, в суффиксе разрешены только определенные символы, не чувствительные к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11197">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11198">ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11198">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11199">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11199">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11200">пространство или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11200">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11201">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11201">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11202">пространство или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11202">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11203">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11203">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11204">пространство или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11204">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11205">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11205">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11206">пространство или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11206">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11207">"A", "B", "C" или "D"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11207">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11208">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11208">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11209">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11209">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11210">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11210">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11211">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11211">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11212">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11212">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11213">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11213">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11214">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11214">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11215">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11215">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. NINO -->
    <Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11216">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11216">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11217">Keyword_uk_nino</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11217">Keyword_uk_nino</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11218">national insurance number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11218">national insurance number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11219">national insurance contributions</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11219">national insurance contributions</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11220">protection act</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11220">protection act</span></span>

## <a name="uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11237">U.K.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11237">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11238">Уникальный номер ссылки на налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11238">Unique Taxpayer Reference Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11239">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11239">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11240">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11240">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11241">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11241">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11242">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11242">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11243">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11243">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11244">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11244">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11245">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11245">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11246">10 цифр без пробелов и делимитеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11246">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11247">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11247">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11248">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11248">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11249">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11249">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11250">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11250">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11251">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11251">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11252">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11252">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11253">Функция находит  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11253">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11254">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11254">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11255">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11255">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11261">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11261">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11262">нет налога #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11262">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11263">нет налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11263">tax no</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11265">таксомоторный #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11265">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11266">taxidno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11266">taxidno#</span></span>

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11274">Номер банковского счета в США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11274">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11275">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11275">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11276">6-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11276">6-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11277">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11277">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11278">6-17 последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11278">6-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11279">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11279">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11280">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11280">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11281">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11281">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11282">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11282">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11283">регулярное выражение Regex_usa_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11283">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11284">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_usa_Bank_Account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11284">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11314">Номер водительских прав в США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11314">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11315">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11315">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11316">Зависит от штата.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11316">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11317">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11317">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11318">зависит от состояния , например, Нью-Йорка:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11318">depends on the state - for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11319">девять цифр, форматированные как ddd ddd ddd ddd, будут соответствовать.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11319">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11320">девять цифр, таких как dddddddd, не совпадают.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11320">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11321">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11321">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11322">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11322">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11323">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11323">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11324">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11324">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11325">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11325">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11326">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11326">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11327">обнаружено ключевое слово из списка Keyword_us_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11327">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11328">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11328">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11329">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11329">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11330">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11330">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11331">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11331">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11332">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11332">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11430">Индивидуальный идентификационный номер налогоплательщика США (ITIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11430">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11431">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11431">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11432">девять цифр, которые начинаются с "9" и содержат "7" или "8" в виде четвертой цифры, необязательно форматированные с пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11432">nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11433">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11433">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11434">форматированный:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11434">formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11435">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11435">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11436">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11436">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11437">пространство или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11437">a space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11438">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11438">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11439">цифру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11439">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11440">пространство или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11440">a space, or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11441">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11441">four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11442">unformatted:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11442">unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11443">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11443">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11444">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11444">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11445">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11445">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11446">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11446">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11447">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11447">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11448">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11448">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11449">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11449">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11450">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11450">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11451">Функция Func_formatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11451">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11452">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11452">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11453">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11453">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11454">Функция Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11454">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11455">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11455">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11456">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11456">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11457">Функция Func_formatted_itin или Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11457">The function Func_formatted_itin or Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
    <Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11458">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11458">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11459">Keyword_itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11459">Keyword_itin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11460">налогоплательщик</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11460">taxpayer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11462">tax identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11462">tax identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11463">itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11463">itin</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11464">i.t.i.n.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11464">i.t.i.n.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11465">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11465">ssn</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11469">itins</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11469">itins</span></span>

## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11472">Номер социального обеспечения США (SSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11472">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11473">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11473">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11474">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11474">nine digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11475">Есть SSN выдан до середины 2011 г., он отличается строгим форматированием, при котором определенные части номера должны входить в указанные диапазоны (при этом нет контрольной суммы).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11475">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11476">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11476">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11477">четыре функции искать SSNs в четырех различных шаблонов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11477">four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11478">Func_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием с тире или пробелами, выданные до 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11478">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11479">Func_unformatted_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием, выданные до 2011 г. (без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр — ццццццццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11479">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11480">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит SSN с тире или пробелами, выданные после 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11480">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11481">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит SSN без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр, выданные после 2011 г. (ццццццццц).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11481">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11482">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11482">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11483">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11483">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11484">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11484">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11485">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11485">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11486">Функция Func_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11486">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11487">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11487">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11488">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11488">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11489">Функция Func_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11489">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11490">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11490">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11491">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11491">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11492">Функция Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11492">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11493">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11493">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11494">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11494">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11495">Функция Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11495">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11496">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11496">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11497">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11497">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11498">Keyword_ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11498">Keyword_ssn</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11499">Номер SSA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11499">SSA Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11500">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11500">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11501">социальное обеспечение #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11501">social security #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11502">социальное обеспечение #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11502">social security#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11503">социального обеспечения нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11503">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11504">Social Security#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11504">Social Security#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11505">Soc Sec</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11505">Soc Sec</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11506">SSN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11506">SSN</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11507">SSNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11507">SSNS</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11508">SSN #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11508">SSN#</span></span>
