## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11511">U.S. / U.K.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11511">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11512">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11512">passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11513">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11513">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11514">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11514">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11515">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11515">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11516">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11516">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11517">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11517">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11518">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11518">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11519">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11519">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11520">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что этот тип конфиденциальной информации обнаружен, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11520">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11521">функция Func_usa_uk_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11521">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11522">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11522">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11523">Найдено `Keywords_eu_passport_date` ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11523">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11524">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11524">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11525">функция Func_usa_uk_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11525">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11526">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` или найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11526">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. / U.K. Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11527">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11527">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11528">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11528">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11529">паспорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11529">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11530">паспорт #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11530">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11531">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11531">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11532">паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11532">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11533">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11533">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11534">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11534">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11535">passportnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11535">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11536">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11536">passport number</span></span>

## <a name="ukraine-passport-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11542">Внутренний паспорт Украины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11542">Ukraine passport domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11543">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11543">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11544">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11544">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11545">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11545">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11546">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11546">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11547">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11547">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11548">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11548">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11549">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11549">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11550">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11550">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11551">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11551">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11552">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11552">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11553">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11553">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11554">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11554">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11555">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11555">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11556">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11556">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11557">В regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11557">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11558">Найдено ключевое слово Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11558">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport Domestic -->
      <Entity id="1817a540-221f-4459-9202-3bd78b81d803" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ukraine-passport-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11567">Паспорт Украины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11567">Ukraine passport international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11568">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только для использования в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11568">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11569">Политики предотвращения потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11569">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11570">политики соответствия требованиям к коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11570">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11571">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11571">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11572">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11572">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11573">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11573">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11574">Формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11574">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11575">альфанумерный шаблон из восьми символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11575">eight-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11576">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11576">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11577">альфанумерный шаблон из восьми символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11577">eight-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11578">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11578">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11579">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11579">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11580">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11580">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11581">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11581">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11582">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11582">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11583">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в непосредственной близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11583">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11584">Regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International контент, который соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11584">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="a59b6-11585">Ключевое слово Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a59b6-11585">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport International -->
      <Entity id="cfbe032d-22e0-4f28-ab68-d66e9641f1e2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
